  "siteName": "InfoQ 中文",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(145, 145, 145);white-space:normal;font-weight:normal;font-size:14px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 14px;margin:13px 0px 0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">整理 | 华卫</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">刚刚，Anthropic 发布了 Claude Haiku 4.5 版本，现已面向所有用户开放。据悉，这是其最小型模型的最新版本，官方宣传其性能与 Sonnet 4 相近，“成本仅为后者的三分之一，速度却超过两倍”。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">Haiku 新版本将立即在 Anthropic 所有免费套餐中上线。该公司认为，新版本对 AI 产品的免费版本而言将具备特殊吸引力，因为它既能提供强大功能，又能将服务器负载降至最低。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">Anthropic 发言人表示，“Haiku 4.5 的发布，意味着所有用户都能通过 Claude.ai 免费使用接近前沿水平的智能。同时，它也为我们的企业客户带来显著优势：Sonnet 4.5 可负责前沿规划，Haiku 4.5 则为子智能体提供支持，打造出多智能体系统，从而快速、高质量地处理复杂重构、迁移及大型功能构建任务。”</span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:14px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 20px;color: #00b38b;text-align: left;line-height: 35px;margin: 40px 8px 0 8px;background: none no-repeat left 28px;background-size: 100% 6px;background-image: url(&quot;https://image.jido.dev/20251017084604_beb661&quot;);\"><span style=\"display: block;font-size: 32px;margin-bottom: 10px;padding-left: 22px;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;更快、更便宜，性能逼近 Sonnet 4 和 GPT-5 </span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">“Haiku 的表现远超其自身定位。”Anthropic 首席产品官 Mike Krieger 在接受采访时表示。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">Haiku 4.5 是一款混合推理模型，这意味着它能够根据处理请求的需求，灵活调整所使用的计算资源量。默认情况下，该模型的算法会通过一套仅需有限硬件资源的工作流程生成响应。用户可开启 “扩展思考”（extended thinking）模式，让 Haiku 4.5 生成更复杂的响应，不过这类响应的生成耗时会更长。据该公司介绍，Haiku 4.5 能够处理包含多达 20 万个 token 信息的多模态提示词。这一能力使其可以处理大型文件，例如篇幅较长的商业文档。该模型每次响应最多可输出 6.4 万个 token。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">Anthropic 表示，这款模型速度更快，性能甚至优于数月前还被视为行业前沿的其他大型模型。例如，在计算机使用能力上，Claude Haiku 4.5 优于该公司 5 月推出的中型模型 Claude Sonnet 4。而在代码生成能力方面，根据用于测试 AI 系统软件编码能力的数据集 SWE-bench Verified 显示，它的表现与 Claude Sonnet 4 以及 OpenAI 最新模型 GPT-5 相近。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">并且，Anthropic 引用了一系列新的基准测试结果来支撑这些性能说法。在该公司的测试中，Haiku 在 SWE-Bench 验证基准测试中得分为 73%，在以命令行为核心的 Terminal-Bench 基准测试中得分为 41%。这一成绩低于 Sonnet 4.5，但在两项测试中均与 Sonnet 4、GPT-5 以及 Gemini 2.5 持平。</span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100162973\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;vertical-align: bottom;height: auto !important;width: 661.003px !important;visibility: visible !important;cursor: auto;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3810728b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOl82xm5CXGxxUOkF2Z5dBpMz6yEvib3VRHONBjnEcoeZOko9YZYmicdqDf9X65P9ENVCznGuGXhO0hw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D1\"></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">测试显示，在工具使用、计算机使用和视觉推理类基准测试中，Haiku 也取得了相近结果。在 OSWorld 基准测试中，Haiku 4.5 得分达 50.7%，显著超过 Sonnet 4 的 42.2%。其在模拟人类计算机操作方面的出色能力，为自动化领域开辟了新可能。借助 Python 工具支持时，该模型数学任务得分达 96.3%；即便不使用工具，也保持着 80.7% 的优异表现。在以终端为核心的编码任务中，Haiku 4.5 得分 41.0%，同样优于 Sonnet 4 的 36.4%。</span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100162970\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"680\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;vertical-align: bottom;height: auto !important;width: 661.003px !important;visibility: visible !important;cursor: auto;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9539b6d1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOl82xm5CXGxxUOkF2Z5dBpMT3kLamWwyOWVQ7D7umJnFkphX3ThrMhGUasJb3qnP81FSSoEzJVFLQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D2\"></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">此外，Anthropic 对 Haiku 4.5 开展了一系列详细的安全性与对齐性评估。该模型的风险行为发生率较低，且对齐表现显著优于其前代产品 Haiku 3.5。在自动对齐评估中，Haiku 4.5 的总体未对齐行为率在统计上也显著低于 Sonnet 4.5 和 Opus 4.1。该公司称，“以这一指标衡量，Claude Haiku 4.5 成为了我们目前最安全的模型。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">现在，Haiku 4.5 已在全平台上线。作为开发者，只需在 Claude API 中调用 claude-haiku-4-5 即可使用。其定价为每百万输入 tokens 1 美元，每百万输出 tokens 5 美元。相比之下， &nbsp;Sonnet 4.5 的价格是其三倍，其定价为每百万输入 tokens 3 美元、每百万输出 tokens 15 美元；而 Opus 4.1 的定价更高，为每百万输入 tokens 15 美元、每百万输出 tokens 75 美元。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">值得一提的是，有用户测试后反馈，“‘两倍多速度’其实还是低估 Haiku 了，说实话。我搭建了一个能直接对比 Sonnet 和 Haiku 4.5 的方法，发现 Haiku 4.5 速度大概是前者的 3.5 倍。而且用户体验感要好得多，因为 Haiku 能始终保持在‘流畅响应区间’内。”</span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100162969\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4832298136645963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"805\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;vertical-align: bottom;height: auto !important;width: 661.003px !important;visibility: visible !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=61f13900&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FZBjVrHIdkOl82xm5CXGxxUOkF2Z5dBpMibx3f8A4enhDCeY4j4ic9FZrmvdeXA2Y6QsPPgB5gSVCTym6xQLOMfUQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwebp%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D3\"></p>\n  <div style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:14px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 20px;color: #00b38b;text-align: left;line-height: 35px;margin: 40px 8px 0 8px;background: none no-repeat left 28px;background-size: 100% 6px;background-image: url(&quot;https://image.jido.dev/20251017084604_beb661&quot;);\"><span style=\"display: block;font-size: 32px;margin-bottom: 10px;padding-left: 22px;\"><span leaf=\"\">2</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;“解锁了一整套全新应用场景” </span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">Haiku 4.5 的发布，延续了 Anthropic 近期一系列备受关注的产品发布节奏：两周前，该公司刚推出 Sonnet 4.5；两个月前，推出了 Opus 4.1。这两款产品在发布时均被赞誉为 “行业领先水平”。而 Haiku 的上一个版本发布于 2024 年 10 月。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">该公司表示，Sonnet 4.5 仍是 Anthropic 性能最强的模型，而 Haiku 4.5 则为用户提供了新选择：当用户希望获得接近前沿的性能，同时又追求更高成本效益时，它便是理想之选。“即便对我个人使用而言，尽管它不如 Sonnet 智能，但我在 Claude 上已开始默认使用它，尤其是在移动应用端 —— 因为它能快得多地给出答案。” Krieger 说道。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">此外，该模型的轻量级特性意味着，更易于并行部署多个 Haiku 智能体，或与更复杂的模型搭配使用。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">例如，在多模型协同使用方面，Sonnet 4.5 可将复杂问题拆解为多步骤计划，随后协调多个 Haiku 4.5 模型组成 “团队”，并行完成各项子任务。Krieger 指出，让这两款模型协同工作，对希望借助 AI 处理长期项目的企业而言尤为实用。“企业可让 Haiku 监控金融数据流 —— 由于它体型更小、成本更低、速度更快，能处理更大体量的数据 —— 随后将初步洞察结果移交 Sonnet，由后者进行更深入的分析。” 他解释道。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">Informa TechTarget 旗下子公司 Omdia 的分析师 Lian Jye Su 表示，Anthropic 设计 Haiku 的初衷显然就是为了辅助 Sonnet，“这样能带来高得多的成本效益比” 。他补充称，若用户选择通过大型模型 Sonnet 运行 AI 项目，会导致 token 消耗量大幅增加，成本也随之升高；相比之下，将任务分配给 Haiku 这类小型模型，性价比会更高。使用 AI 技术的企业应从一开始就明白，AI 工作流十分复杂，需做好准备，通过混合使用大型与小型模型来提升成本效益。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">Futurum Group 分析师 David Nicholson 则对于 Sonnet 4.5 与 Haiku 4.5 之间 “分工协作” 的能力提出了一些疑问：“它们如何拆分任务，又如何确保原始目标的完整性不受影响？每个 Haiku 实例都会生成独特的数据，执行子任务的所有 Haiku 实例，是否能知晓其他实例的工作内容？将一项任务拆分为子任务的效率，又存在哪些局限？”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">Krieger 表示，Haiku 将首次让全新的生产环境部署模式成为可能。“它为生产环境中的 AI 开辟了全新应用领域 ——Sonnet 负责复杂规划，而由 Haiku 驱动的子智能体则快速执行任务，我们为用户提供了一套完整的智能体工具库，其中每个模型都针对任务的不同环节，具备了智能、速度与成本的最优组合。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">Haiku 4.5 最直接的应用场景还可能出现在软件开发工具领域。Claude Code 已在该领域广泛使用，而延迟往往是该领域的关键影响因素。在 Anthropic 提供的声明中，Zencoder 首席执行官 Andrew Filev 将 Haiku 新版本描述为 “解锁了一整套全新应用场景”。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">目前，已有多家企业接入 Haiku 4.5 并反馈了积极效果。代码初创公司 Augment 的联合创始人 Guy Gur-Ari 表示，该模型 “达到了我们此前认为不可能的平衡点：接近前沿水平的代码生成质量，兼具极快的速度与成本效益”。在 Augment 的内部测试中，Haiku 4.5 实现了 Sonnet 4.5 90% 的性能，同时表现与规模大得多的模型相当。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">另一家聚焦代码领域的初创公司 Windsurf 首席执行官 Jeff Wang 称，Haiku 4.5 “模糊了” 速度、成本与质量之间传统权衡的界限。“它是一款兼具速度与前沿性能的模型，同时保持了成本效率，也预示了这类模型的发展方向。”演示软件公司 Gamma 的联合创始人 Jon Noronha 表示，Haiku 4.5“在幻灯片文本生成的指令遵循能力上，表现优于我们当前使用的模型：准确率达 65%，而我们付费层级模型的准确率为 44%。 这对我们的单位经济效益而言，是颠覆性的改变”。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:14px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 20px;color: #00b38b;text-align: left;line-height: 35px;margin: 40px 8px 0 8px;background: none no-repeat left 28px;background-size: 100% 6px;background-image: url(&quot;https://image.jido.dev/20251017084604_beb661&quot;);\"><span style=\"display: block;font-size: 32px;margin-bottom: 10px;padding-left: 22px;\"><span leaf=\"\">3</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;5 个月成本暴跌 2/3，AI 经济逻辑正惊人转变 </span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">此次模型发布之际，Anthropic 的业务正呈爆发式增长。据该公司发言人称，其月度年化收入即将突破 70 亿美元，而 8 月公布的这一数据还仅为 50 多亿美元。路透社获取的内部预测显示，Anthropic 设定的 2026 年年化收入目标为 200 亿至 260 亿美元，较当前水平增幅将超过 200%，接近 300%。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">目前，Anthropic 服务的企业客户已超 30 万家，企业级产品收入约占总营收的 80%。在其旗下最成功的产品中，代码生成工具 Claude Code 表现尤为突出 —— 自今年早些时候推出以来，该工具的年化收入已接近 10 亿美元。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">“我们现在确实是火力全开。” Krieger 表示。据了解，行业的极速发展，让 Anthropic 在每次产品发布后都没有太多时间安于现状。该公司在训练 Sonnet 4.5 的同时，就已启动了 Haiku 4.5 的研发工作。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">Krieger 将过去两年描述为 “AI 错失恐惧期”，期间企业纷纷采用 AI 工具，却缺乏清晰的成功衡量标准；而如今，企业开始要求获得可量化的投资回报。在 “Superhuman AI” 播客节目中，他表示：“优秀的产品必须有某种成功指标或评估标准作为支撑。在与部署 AI 的企业交流时，我多次发现了这一点。”对于评估 AI 工具的企业而言，其考量越来越聚焦于具体的生产力提升。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">五个月前，Sonnet 4 的能力还需高价获取，且代表行业前沿；如今，Haiku 4.5 能以三分之一的成本提供相近性能。短短五个月内，AI 性能保持稳定，价格降了原先的三分之二 。若这一趋势持续（从 Anthropic 的发布节奏，以及来自 OpenAI、谷歌的竞争压力来看，这种可能性很大），那么如今看似先进的 AI 能力，一年内可能会变得常规且廉价。AI 的基本经济逻辑正以惊人速度发生转变。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">当前，Anthropic 估值达 1830 亿美元。Anthropic 正紧追谷歌、OpenAI 等竞争对手 —— 其中 OpenAI 的估值已飙升至 5000 亿美元。自今年 8 月推出 GPT-5 后，OpenAI 已签署多项数十亿美元规模的基础设施协议，并发布了名为 Sora 的短视频应用。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">但 Jye Su 认为，“如今所有模型都处于迭代优化中，遗憾的是，即便在所有头部厂商的产品之间，也没有哪项特性真正脱颖而出。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">企业最终会选择 Claude，还是 OpenAI、谷歌及其他不断涌现的竞争对手提供的、能力日益强大的产品，目前仍是未知数。但 Anthropic 正明确押注：AI 的未来不属于那些能打造出单一最强模型的企业，而属于那些能以合适的价格、合适的速度提供合适智能，并让所有人都能获取的企业。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: bold;\">参考链接：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://www.anthropic.com/news/claude-haiku-4-5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.anthropic.com/news/claude-haiku-4-5</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2025/10/15/anthropic-launches-new-version-of-scaled-down-haiku-model/\" target=\"_blank\">https://techcrunch.com/2025/10/15/anthropic-launches-new-version-of-scaled-down-haiku-model/</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://aibusiness.com/generative-ai/anthropic-launches-claude-haiku-4-5-a-small-model-\" target=\"_blank\">https://aibusiness.com/generative-ai/anthropic-launches-claude-haiku-4-5-a-small-model-</a></span><a class=\"wx_topic_link\" topic-id=\"mgswq4ry-ku9ma3\" style=\"color: #576B95 !important;\" data-topic=\"1\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">#close</span></a><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">-modal</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://venturebeat.com/ai/anthropic-is-giving-away-its-powerful-claude-haiku-4-5-ai-for-free-to-take\" target=\"_blank\">https://venturebeat.com/ai/anthropic-is-giving-away-its-powerful-claude-haiku-4-5-ai-for-free-to-take</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Anthropic 发布 Claude Haiku 4.5 模型，以更低成本和更快速度，实现接近前沿大模型的性能，并开启多智能体系统新应用。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Anthropic 发布 Claude Haiku 4.5 模型，以更低成本和更快速度，实现接近前沿大模型的性能，并开启多智能体系统新应用。",
  "summary": "Anthropic 近日推出其最小型模型 Claude Haiku 的最新版本 Haiku 4.5，现已面向所有用户开放。该模型官方宣称其在部分基准测试中性能与 Sonnet 4 相近，甚至在某些方面与 GPT-5 持平，但成本仅为后者的三分之一，速度提升两倍以上（用户实测达 3.5 倍）。Haiku 4.5 是一款混合推理模型，支持高达 20 万 token 输入和 6.4 万 token 输出的多模态提示词。在 SWE-bench Verified、Terminal-Bench 和 OSWorld 等基准测试中，其表现与 Sonnet 4、GPT-5 及 Gemini 2.5 持平或超越，尤其在计算机使用能力上表现出色。Anthropic 强调 Haiku 4.5 在安全性与对齐性方面也显著优于前代，是目前最安全的模型。该模型定价极具竞争力，每百万输入 token 1 美元，输出 token 5 美元。Haiku 4.5 的发布，不仅为免费用户提供了前沿智能，更通过其轻量、高效的特性，解锁了多智能体系统、混合模型协同等全新应用场景，例如与 Sonnet 4.5 配合处理复杂任务。文章指出，此次发布预示着 AI 经济逻辑的惊人转变，即先进 AI 能力正变得更加廉价和普及。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Claude Haiku 4.5 以显著的成本和速度优势，提供了接近前沿大模型的性能。",
      "explanation": "该模型在基准测试中表现与 Sonnet 4 和 GPT-5 相当，但成本仅为 Sonnet 4.5 的三分之一，用户实测速度更是高达 3.5 倍，极大降低了高性能 AI 的门槛。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Haiku 4.5 的轻量、高效和低成本特性，开启了多智能体系统和混合模型协同的新应用模式。",
      "explanation": "其高效率和低成本使其能作为子智能体与更复杂的模型（如 Sonnet 4.5）协同工作，处理大规模数据监控和复杂任务分解，优化企业 AI 工作流。"
    },
    {
      "point": "此次模型发布预示着 AI 经济逻辑正发生根本性转变，先进 AI 能力日益普及和廉价。",
      "explanation": "过去昂贵的前沿 AI 能力，在短短数月内成本大幅下降，性能保持稳定，这促使企业更加关注 AI 的量化投资回报，推动 AI 技术向更广泛的生产环境渗透。"
    }
